      <section eId="sec_18_2_20">
        <num>18-2-20</num>
        <content>
          <p>The rights of creditors shall be favored by the courts; and every remedy and facility shall be afforded them to detect, defeat, and annul any effort to defraud them of their just rights.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 1947; Code 1868, § 1935; Code 1873, § 1945; Code 1882, § 1945; Civil Code 1895, § 2687; Civil Code 1910, § 3216; Code 1933, § 28-102.)</p>
